## Project Overview

The **AI Smartphone Recommender** is a web-based application that helps users find the best smartphone based on their preferences.
It combines:

- Classic feature-based scoring (price, RAM, battery, camera, display, weight, release year)
- Semantic natural language understanding
- Satisfaction-driven recommendation (user preference optimization)

The system also provides **explainable recommendations**, showing why each phone was chosen and highlighting strengths and weaknesses.

---

## Features

- Multi-mode recommendation engine:
  - **Fast / Local (Classic)**
  - **Semantic AI-powered**
  - **Satisfaction-focused**
- **Brand-aware recommendations** with fuzzy matching
- **Explainability bars** for each feature
- **Performance-profile weighting** (Balanced / Performance / Battery-first)
- Cold-start handling for new users
- Dataset health diagnostics endpoint
- 3D model viewer for phones (optional)
- Safe error handling with zero crashes
- Responsive and visually polished frontend

